Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing this didn't burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.72,0:00:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our prey, to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.39,0:00:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I could let them take\N300 barrel of dragon oil from\Nunder our noses!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll finish it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.47,0:00:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:00:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Those jerks just added\Nmore fuel to the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.01,0:00:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Engine room! How long until takeoff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.73,0:01:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do more than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How the fuck isn't it dead\Nafter all those bombs?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.01,0:01:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be dead with all the poison,\NI can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...! There is the...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.20,0:01:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We shook it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... thanks for doing something stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.01,0:02:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan begins now!\NBe on time for once in your lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.93,0:02:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddamnit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's our time to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.10,0:02:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure this was\Nbecause we let our guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we barely knew anything\Nabout how dragons lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This tragedy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Was something we drakers\Nbrought upon ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.58,0:02:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... what a terrible sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't aim with so many obstacles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise our course and find me a place\Nwith a clear line of fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? What happened to the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the middle of the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a place like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't tell there was\Na town here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,At least it seems that\Nall the people here evacuated safely...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Jiro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't fly anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put it out of its misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that building over there\Nan oil refinery?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It if catches fire all this area\Nwill be a sea of flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ah...\N-Mika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't help it! We'll finish it\Noff right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Vadakin! You and the rest go\Nsurround it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood! You guys, come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah!\N-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's all cover Mika!\N-Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem to do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is the\Nair team doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it because the dragon is\Nin a place where the Quin Zaza can't aim?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't think we would be\Nfighting in the middle of the streets!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! That Gibbs,\Nwhat shitty plan is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost out of bomb lances!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This big bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case how about switching to\Nstun lances, Takita?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Vannie-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, work...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The bullets we are firing\Ncan't cause it to bleed enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They aren't even breaking\Nthrough its skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What a waste... these aren't cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If guns don't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll go with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he planning to stab that monster\Nwith only a spear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika is going there, don't fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:06:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't run anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Niko! Cover me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey! Don't give me that you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he starting to act like Mika?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mika!\N-Mika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I told ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:07:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're bleeding a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring me... bring me a spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?\NYou can't go with that wound!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's already
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,one of our spears stabbed in its body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's our prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We must hunt it properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And eat it whole!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hunt, dissect and eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all drakers are about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,See? You can't go like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! This looks bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to burn all of us\Nwith its heat ray!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-What the hell's that?\N-Looks dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wait, wait, wait!\N-This again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Evade its line of fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it aiming though?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... we failed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... Jiro-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... what the hell is he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's climbing onto the dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Jiro-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's... no time to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:09:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.02,0:10:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Jiro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I run after all of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If I shoot the weak point\Nin its spine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's at point-blank...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet... I can't give up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Jirooo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Quin Zaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Do this more carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you plan to wreck the ship\Nor what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocco-san, didn't you tell me\Nto ram it without fear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I did say to ram it but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say it was okay to\Nbreak the ship in half!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do one without the other!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to fall apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick! Reverse the engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Cha-changing gears!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah! We're falling down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Increasing power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:12:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Niko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-We did it!\N-Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They pulled quite a stunt...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine what Lee-san\Nis gonna say about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro! Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You attracted its attention\Nflawlessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-It is really over?\N-Did they kill it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! The city's all ruins now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! My precious bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit... why did this happen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end... we needed\Neach and every spear to finish it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're pretty sloppy drakers, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... all this bleeding...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts like hell
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh... our poor little ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you taking the ship for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The airscrews are fine!\NYou can fly away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.58,0:14:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing damage control as\Nsoon as we dock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...? Katja!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.64,0:14:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so worried when I saw\Nthe bar destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone evacuated and we're\Nsafe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank god...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't exagerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Really worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A-... about everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That brat! As soon as I take\Nmy eyes off him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting a head start, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad for him, the scoundrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Waah! What a pretty girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So... without further ado!\NA little kiss of reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... wai- Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't treat a customer like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't move anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys put it down finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... you can say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I look at it closely\Nit's pretty frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna dissect it right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:16:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But, since it has poison in its\Nsystem and we fired stun lances at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we dissect it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not good enough to sell it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But its value has gone down\Nquite considerably.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Though that's only a problem\Nwe have to face ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Value... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A fight? I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of your "little" mistake\Nthe city has suffered a tragedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You are able to fly in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,because this city buys all it can\Nfrom you, drakers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And you thank us like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If we didn't bring dragons here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the ones who couldn't live\Nwould be you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We are always risking our lives\Nup there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh! Now you've said it!\NWho do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop it! This is not the time\Nto be fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?\NAre you one of his friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I am his friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I am a draker too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:17:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying it's that lil' puny ship\Nof yours who caught it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying anything like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look good...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The city of Quon is a very\Nimportant place as a base for drakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want them to hold a grudge\Nagainst us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, rather than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If things remain like this,\Nno one here will buy this dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Bunch of idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you causing problems\Nto these people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you can walk like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can worry about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go causing unnecesary problems,\Nyou damn spineless rubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have energy to pick fights\Nyou'd better use it to pick debris instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But... that's not the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't give a damn\Nabout your excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that dealing with incompetent\Ncrew looks the same wherever you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there are people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ah? And you're one of them!\N-Oh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirmed incompetent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was not for this boy,\Nyou'd probably all be dead by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If another heat ray went off...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The destruction wouldn't have ended here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But... the damages are so serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-Gibbs-san.\N-Mmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's donate the dragon to the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Lee-san, what the hell are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides the damages to the city\Nbeing so serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If we were to take advantage of the situation\Nand profit, it's the same as asking for a rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The real good deal for us is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,To trade the dragon in exchange for\Nship repairs and the rest of the expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not see how difficult was\Nfor us to take that dragon down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't see a single coin\Nif we can't sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I wonder what Crocco\Nwould say if he knew this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocco!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as they repair our\Nship, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... not much we can do\Nabout it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.26,0:18:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh... what a waste of effort...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's call it even for both of us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It better be enough food\Nfor me after this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All this bleeding made me hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I think losing blood has nothing to do\Nwith being hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be at Gramps Ura's place\Neating some meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! We are going to clean up\Nthe city too, Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm injured, goddamnit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the strength of\Nan injured man, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Shut your mouth and come!\N-As pleasant as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmmm... I think he'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief... they are always\Ncausing problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they are your friends\Nafter all, Jiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a good bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Katja, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The festival...\NWe pretty much ruined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after I promised you\Nwe'd come together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:21:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face was so serious,\NI couldn't hold my laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-But...\N-Mmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure wanted to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment you hunted\Nthe dragon, Jiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
